<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.cair.zen;3;59447" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PSI6,680;PCairZen3,59447</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Ζήνωνι χαίρειν Θέων <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὁ συσ</supplied>ταθεὶ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς ὑπ᾽</supplied> Ἐφαρμόστου τοῦ μακα-

    <lb n="2"/>ρίτου. τὰ μὲν ἄλλα χάριν ἔχω πάσης πολυωρίας παρὰ σοῦ τυγ-

    <lb n="3"/>χάνων, ἀξιῶ δέ σε, εἰ καί σοι φαίνομαι μέτρια λέγειν, τάξαι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">με</unclear> 

    <lb n="4"/>ἐπί τινος, ὅπως ἄν σοι χρείας παρέχωμαι ὑπουργῶν ἀμέμπτως 

    <lb n="5"/>τὸ προστασσόμενον, ἵνα ἐγώ τε τ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὰ</unclear> παρὰ σοῦ διδόμενα λαμ-

    <lb n="6"/>βάνω δικαιότερον, σύ τε ἥδιον διδῶις ποιοῦντός τι ἐμοῦ πλέον σοι. 

    <lb n="7"/>εἰ δ᾽ ἐπὶ τοῦ παρόντος ἡσυχίαν ἄγειν κελεύεις, <choice><corr>τὸν</corr><sic>τομ</sic></choice> μὲν καιρὸν αὐτὸς 

    <lb n="8"/>εἰδήσεις, ἐμοὶ δὲ <subst><add place="inline">καλῶς</add><del rend="corrected">κα<del rend="erasure">ι</del>λως</del></subst> ἂν ποιήσαις συντάξας ὅπως ἂν παρα-

    <lb n="9"/>δειχθῆι μεθ᾽ ὧν οἰκίαν τε ἕξω καὶ τὰ λοιπὰ δέοντα, ἵνα μὴ πρεσ-

    <lb n="10"/>βύτερος ὢν ῥέμβωμαι. πρὸς ἕτερον γὰρ οὐθένα καταφυ-

    <lb n="11"/>γεῖν ἐστί μοι καλῶς ἐχον, ἐξ ἀρχῆς σοι <add place="supralinear">μου</add> <subst><add place="inline">συσταθέντος</add><del rend="corrected">συν<del rend="erasure">απ<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/></del>συσταθεντος</del></subst>. </ab></div><div n="meta.1476" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.1476" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notBefore="-0243-09-17" type="textDate">nach 17. Sept. 243 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.1476" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. P.Lugd. Bat. XXI A, S. 110 und 121.</p></div><div n="meta.1476" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">5</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59852</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">1476</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">5</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59852</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;5;59852" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.1476" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">X</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">38</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.1476" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">PSI VI 680: ZPE 100, 1994, Tafel IX</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.1476" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Cair. Zen. III 59447</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">PSI VI 680 (Z. 1 - 11 teilweise)</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">C.Pap. Hen